reviewText: I love the Meatballs series and I think this sequel does it justice. I'm a huge Corey fan and so it gets an extra star from me for that haha. Besides that, I enjoy the corny antics along with the good storyline it brings out.

reviewText: Meatballs 4 with Corey Feldman is a very funny movie.  I've just been told that it is FINALLY..........FINALLY going to be REreleased as a DVD in AMERICA!!!!!  So look for it on August 28th.  Hopefully once IT becomes a DVD whoever is releasing it, ought to RErelease the other two.  I think they ought to call it "THE MEATBALLS MEATPACK" where ALL four Meatball movies are contained in the collection.  This particular Meatballs movie is the best Corey Feldman is great in it.

reviewText: My favourite movies are camp movies.  It is about a successful camp.  But their is another camp, then wants it to go bust.  So they do things to erode the campers satisfaction.  Camp movies are great as they are, but this one has something else that makes it more interesting.Meatballs 4

reviewText: A slapstick comedy based on a summer camp trip fun. A truly fun time and the cast of characters involved in the mischief that ensues is hilarious! A great story about keeping summer camps open, fun, and where memories are made great ones and not so memorable ones.
